title: Bahamas Consumer Price Index Cpi
description: Consumer Price Index CPI in Bahamas remained unchanged at 119.30 points in August from 119.30 points in July of 2022. Consumer Price Index CPI in Bahamas averaged 90.20 points from 1995 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 119.30 points in July of 2022 and a record low of 70.39 points in January of 1995. This page provides - Bahamas Consumer Price Index Cpi- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Department of Statistics of The Bahamas
